sequenceDiagram
  actor Client
  participant API as graphify-api
  participant NATS as NATS JetStream
  participant Cloner as graphify-cloner
  participant Worker as graphify-worker
  participant FS as data/repos (shared vol)

  Client->>API: POST /api/v1/repositories {githubRepoUrl}
  API->>FS: Store.Create -> writeAtomic(metadata=queued)
  API->>NATS: publish clone.requested (msgId clone-request:id)
  API-->>Client: 202 {id, statusUrl}
  NATS->>Cloner: deliver clone.requested
  Cloner->>FS: git clone --depth 1 -> rename tmp -> repository/
  Cloner->>FS: Store.Update -> writeAtomic(status=cloned, resolvedSha)
  Cloner->>NATS: publish cloned
  NATS->>Worker: deliver cloned
  Worker->>FS: graphify extract --code-only -> graphify-out/graph.json
  Worker->>FS: Store.Update -> writeAtomic(status=ready, artifacts[])
  Worker->>NATS: publish graph.ready
  loop poll until ready
    Client->>API: GET /api/v1/repositories/{id}
    API->>FS: Store.Get -> readUnlocked(metadata.json)
    API-->>Client: {status}
  end
  Client->>API: GET /api/v1/repositories/{id}/download?format=zip
  API->>FS: artifacts.Zip(repoDir, items)
  API-->>Client: 200 application/zip
